Title: The Land of Mystical Things
DateModified: '2019-02-27'
DatePublished: '2019-02-27'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/the-land-of-mystical-things
SetInCountry: Indonesia
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Tharsya Rieskyanna
AuthorCountry: Indonesia
Text: 'This story about Indonesia. An archipelago who have a thousand of island and
  more. Here, the people are living in peace. But, sadly something bothering their
  peacefullness. A group of mean and selfish human are attacking the peace and prosperity
  that known for a thousand hundred years of time. In this story, our local heroes
  will making a true connection with Indonesian people. Regarding their tribe, gender,
  economy and social backgound, also their religion. The readers will ''see and feel''
  this magnificent island and make true connection also, with its magical surroundings,
  land, sea, and in the end what really connect all human: is about LOVE. Love for
  nature, love for earth, love for humanity, love for The Almighty God, and the love
  for yourself and family.'
